	<p>Bar magnets have a physical property called the magnetic moment.</p>
	
	<definition>
		<title>Magnetic Moment</title>
		<statement>
			<p>The <term>magnetic moment</term>, <m>\vec{\mu}</m>, points from the south to the north pole inside a bar magnet.</p>
		</statement>
	</definition>
	
